desc: Arm Candy jewelry delivers a sense of effortless elegance. Each piece is handcrafted and designed using the highest quality materials to suit anyone for any occasion. Bracelets can be mixed + matched, stacked + layered or worn on their own. From 14k gold to pave diamonds, the line delivers a modern twist on simplicity.

layout.text: A modern twist on simplicity. Collectable pieces to layer, mix & match.
